text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21164,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/11\/10\/purpose-learning-taqwa-righteousness\/","url_meta":{"origin":34832,"position":2},"title":"Sufyan on Knowledge: Purpose of learning is to be God-fearing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Abdul Barr reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cSurely, sacred knowledge is only studied to become mindful of Allah. Knowledge is only favored over other virtues because it makes one fearful of Allah.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u02bb Baya\u0304n al-\u02bbIlm li-Ibn 'Abd al-Barr 1159 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36611,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/06\/fear-allah-listen-obey\/","url_meta":{"origin":34832,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Rulers: Fear Allah, listen, and obey lawful orders","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Adi ibn Hatim reported: We said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, we do not ask you about obedience to Godfearing rulers, but rather those who do this and that,\u201d and he mentioned their evil. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFear Allah, listen, and obey.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/05\/hasan-bored-ibadah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34832,"position":4},"title":"Hasan on Arguing: They were bored with worship, so they argued","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ahmad ibn Hanbal reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, heard some people arguing and he said, \u201cBy Allah! These are not but people who are bored with worship and they found speaking easier upon them than acting. Their piety diminished and thus they speak.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ah\u0323mad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26949,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/30\/ibrahim-freedom-content-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34832,"position":5},"title":"Ibrahim on Contentment: Spiritual freedom is satisfaction with decree of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: Ibrahim ibn Shayban, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \"Dignity is in humility, honor is in righteousness, and freedom is in contentment.\" Source:\u00a0Mada\u0304rij al-Sa\u0304liki\u0304n 2\/314 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u064a\u0645 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0634\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0641\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0636\u064f\u0639\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0632